---
title: Cheesy Beef & Haloumi Burger with Fries, Caramelised Onion Chutney & Mayonnaise
description: Get your napkins ready – this is one seriously juicy burger! We've loaded it with flavour, from the rosemary-infused
caramelised onion chutney to the truffle mayo and melted Cheddar, so that every bite will take you to your happy place.
